This Resource describes functions for the control and monitoring of
The circuit breaker status. The status can only be reset out of
The rated current in Ampere, defined at manufacturing time.
The rated breaking current in Ampere, defined at manufacturing time.
The rated voltage in Volts, defined at manufacturing time.
Insulation resistance of circuit breaker (M Ohm).
An RFC3339 formatted time indicating when the data was observed
